sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Okta Inc (Symbol: OKTA), where a total volume of 9,680 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 968,000 underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 48.1% of OKTA's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 2.0 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $100 strike put option expiring January 17, 2020, with 1,000 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 100,000 underlying shares of OKTA.
